HEADWORD: Alar
<hw>A"lar</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>alarius</ets>, fr. <ets>ala</ets> wing: cf. F.
<ets>alaire</ets>.]</ety> <sn>1.</sn> <def>Pertaining to, or having,
